channel.description: How would I make the client HD? Like a 562 it has really good graphics but my Project insanity has shit graphics that piss me off. I am willing to spend loads of time making to better quality if someone could guide me to a tutorial or get me started?

item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

Travas:

If you want a HD game, just play a higher revision

That’s not needed at all. You would just need the prior knowledge to actually change the methods and etc and make your client load a higher cache. For time’s sake, it would be faster to just find a higher revision.
